    <item>
      <title>LG能源与WesCEF签署第二份协议以扩大锂供应</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/lg-energy-signs-2nd-agreement-with-wescef-expand-lithium-supply-2024-02-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国 LG Energy Solution 周二与澳大利亚 Wesfarmers Chemicals、Energy and Fertilizers (WesCEF) 签署了第二份承购协议，以扩大其锂采购供应链。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/lg-energy-signs-2nd-agreement-with-wescef-expand-lithium-supply-2024-02-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 00:57:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>恶劣天气导致澳大利亚断电并引发丛林大火</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/strong-winds-cause-power-outages-fan-bushfires-australias-southeast-2024-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，澳大利亚维多利亚州数十万居民仍然断电，恶劣天气导致输电线路瘫痪，并引发丛林大火，导致五名消防员受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/strong-winds-cause-power-outages-fan-bushfires-australias-southeast-2024-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 23:15:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赌场运营商米高梅因中国旅游反弹而超出第四季度预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/casino-operator-mgm-beats-fourth-quarter-estimates-china-travel-rebound-2024-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[米高梅国际酒店集团周二第四季度业绩超出市场预期，其中国业务受益于博彩中心澳门取消某些与疫情相关的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/casino-operator-mgm-beats-fourth-quarter-estimates-china-travel-rebound-2024-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 23:08:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚投票取代佐科维，洪水扰乱了一些民意调查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-votes-new-president-under-shadow-influential-incumbent-2024-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚人周三开始在群岛各地进行投票，这场选举的主要内容是接替受欢迎的总统佐科·维多多(Joko Widodo)，他的影响力可能决定谁将掌管世界第三大民主国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-votes-new-president-under-shadow-influential-incumbent-2024-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 21:02:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳航部门飞行员将计划的三天罢工延长至六天</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/pilots-qantas-unit-extends-planned-three-day-strike-six-days-2024-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳洲航空包机部门周二表示，飞行员将从本周三开始罢工六天，而不是原计划的三天，因为他们继续要求加薪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/pilots-qantas-unit-extends-planned-three-day-strike-six-days-2024-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 12:21:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国活动人士因“骚扰”皇家车队后因煽动叛乱被捕</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-activists-arrested-sedition-after-harassing-royal-motorcade-2024-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国警方周二逮捕了两名活动人士，罪名是煽动叛乱和计算机犯罪，罪名是涉嫌骚扰曼谷的王室车队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-activists-arrested-sedition-after-harassing-royal-motorcade-2024-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 12:19:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Fortescue Metals 董事长表示，碳捕获技术“完全是谎言”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/carbon-capture-tech-complete-falsehood-says-fortescue-metals-chairman-2024-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Fortescue Metals 执行董事长安德鲁·福雷斯特 (Andrew Forrest) 周二表示，碳捕获并不是能源转型的解决方案，政治领导人需要提供真正的、非绿色化的承诺来鼓励投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/carbon-capture-tech-complete-falsehood-says-fortescue-metals-chairman-2024-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 12:17:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
